<BaseLayout title="About - Weird Science News">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">About Us</h1>
  <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      Welcome to Weird Science News, where we explore the strangest and most fascinating discoveries in the world of science. Our mission is to make complex scientific concepts accessible while highlighting the peculiar and extraordinary aspects of scientific research.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-4">
      From zombie ants to quantum physics paradoxes, we cover the most intriguing stories that showcase the wonderful weirdness of our universe. Our team of writers works hard to bring you accurate, well-researched articles that will both educate and entertain.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
